Usage: generate_esd_rlrp_report [-help] -net <string>
                                [-number_threads <integer>]
                                -state_directory <string>
                                [-instance_pair_list <string> | -instance_pair_list_file <string>]

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-instance_pair_list <string>          # instance pair list {{INST1 INST2 [PIN1
                                      # PIN2]}+} (string, optional)
-instance_pair_list_file <string>     # instance pair list file
                                      # (string, optional)
-net <string>                         # net name (string, required)
-number_threads <integer>             # <number of threads> (int, optional)
-state_directory <string>             # <top level state directory>
                                      # (string, required)